&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;OVERVIEW OF GAMMA ENGINEERING:&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Gamma Engineering team&lt;/strong&gt; is building the next generation of analytics tools:
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
