 &lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;REQUIREMENTS:&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&amp;bull; Masters Degree in Computer Research Science, Statistics, Operations Research, or related field
